description: Safeplus International Holdings Limited develops and markets various technologies for the medical device industries. It is seeking partners to monetize its patented technologies, including biothermal power supply and pulsewidth modulation technology to enhance the performance of pacemakers and neurostimulators, and photonics and nanomaterials patents. The company was formerly known as Biophan Technologies, Inc. and changed its name to Safeplus International Holdings Limited in September 2020. Safeplus International Holdings Limited was founded in 1963 and is based in Pittsford, New York.
